1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 d6 3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 Nf6 5. Nc3 a6
{ The Najdorf Sicilian is one of the most complex openings. There is an immediate imbalance due to the exchange of the c- and d-pawn and White's space advantage. Black will often find active play on the queenside, and White on occasion is forced to resort to drastic measures to keep an advantage or the balance. This course intends to approach the tactical opportunities for both sides. Time to check out typical tactics.    Learning an opening isn't just memorizing variations and understanding the general strategical ideas. In our opinion, you best amplify your knowledge in openings and structures by internalizing the common tactical motifs. This book gives you an overview of the most typical tactics in the Najdorf Sicilian from both the White and the Black side. By learning them you will not only sometimes win a game effortlessly or stop a tactical idea from your opponent you weren't aware of, but you'll also strongly strengthen your understanding of typical Najdorf positions. If you try to understand why and when a certain tactic works, where the typically strong and weak points are, and which pieces might be in danger, you will learn how to set up your pieces harmoniously.    There are two entry chapters with simple puzzles, and then eleven thematic chapters, four of them about typical sacrifices. As this popular opening has often been used by world champions and other world-class players, we compiled a chapter just with combinations of these legends of the game. After these more than 100 exercises, you can test your fresh skills in four test chapters of increasing average difficulty which consists of 20 positions each. Finally, for the fearless, there is a bonus chapter with extremely hard puzzles.    A few words on our approach to finding good and interesting positions. We've developed technology and sophisticated algorithms to automatically find correct and interesting puzzles for various topics. We handpick the best ones and refine the solutions. That means these puzzles are carefully selected by their relevance and cover all frequently occurring tactics. All puzzles have a clear and carefully checked solution.    Enjoy! }
*

