17. Nxg7
{ 17.Nh6+?  Kh8-+   17.Bh6?  g6  18.Bxf8  Kxf8-+   17.Qh4?  Now, Black is quick enough with his counterplay. The computer gives the following variation  17...Nxd3  18.Rxd3  Rc8  19.Rc1  Bxd5  20.Nxg7!  Be4  21.Rg3  Qa5  22.Bxf6  Bxc2+  23.Ka1  Bg6  24.Rb1  Bxf6  25.Qxf6  Qd8  26.Nh5  Qxf6  27.Nxf6+  Kg7  28.Nd5= }
