{ Since Black is often castling late, "King in the middle" is a central theme in the Najdorf. The Black player should know what he can get away with, the White player should know the basic techniques to crack Black's central pawn shield. There are several chapters dedicated to thematic techniques like "Sacrifice on e6" or "Sacrifice on d5/f5". In this chapter you'll find a little less thematic, but still very useful techniques to get to Black's king. }
