19. Nxe6
{ A very typical sac in the Najdorf. White gives a piece to prevent castling. }
19... fxe6 20. Rxe6 Kf7
{ 20...Qc7  21.Rde1  Kf7  22.Rxe7+  Qxe7  23.Rxe7+  Kxe7  24.Qxb4+-  White has too many pawns and Black is too uncoordiated to hold here.   20...Rf8  21.Qxd6  Qd8  22.Qe5+- }
21. Rxe7+ Kxe7 22. Qxd6+
{ White will at least pick up the b7-bishop and still have a crushing attack. }
