{ If there would be a 'Hall of Fame' for chess openings the Najdorf would definitely be one of the handful members. Besides openings like e.g. the Ruy Lopez and Grünfeld, the Najdorf is a battleground of champions and in the arsenal of most elite players for a long time already. In this chapter, we present 'must-know combinations' and combinations of some of the finest Najdorf players. }
