{ White sacrificed a piece to get a dangerous passer on f7 and to hold Black's king in the center. }
22. Nxe5 dxe5 23. Nd5+
{ A little mysterious at first sight. Usually White wants to clear the e-file or the square f5 with this sacrifice, here he has other ideas. }
23... exd5 { 23...Kf8  24.Nb6+-  is hopeless. } 24. Qa3+
{ This is the point. White's queen attacks through the backdoor. } 24... Ke6
25. exd5+ Qxd5 26. Rxd5 *

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
