12. Bxe6 fxe6 13. Nxe6 Nxg3 { 13...Ne5  14.b4  Qb6  15.Nd5+- } 14. fxg3
{ Allowing the f1-rook to come into play.   14.hxg3?  Nf6  15.Nxf8  Rxf8  16.Qxd6  Qd8+= }
14... Ne5 15. Rxf8+ Rxf8 16. Qxd6 Rf6
{ 16...Rf7  17.Nd5+-   16...Bxe6  17.Qxe6+  Kd8  18.Rd1++- } 17. Qc7
