17... Qxc7 { 17...Nc6  18.Qxa5  Nxa5  19.Nc7++-   17...Qb4  18.Nd5+- } 18.
Nxc7+ Kd8 19. Nxa8 *

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
[Date "????.??.??"]
[Round "?"]
[White "Brainteasers"]
[Black "Manik, Mikulas vs. Marek, Matyas"]
[Result "*"]
[FEN "r1b1k2r/1p1n1p2/p3pP1p/2b5/3N3Q/2q5/P1P1B1PP/3R1R1K w kq - 0 21"]
[SetUp "1"]

{ Welcome to the craziest position in this book. White has, as usual, sacrificed a piece to get ahead in development and keep Black's king in the center. }
21. Nxe6 { and there goes another piece. } 21... fxe6 22. Rd3
{ Preparing to transfer the rook via the 3rd rank.  Starting with   22.f7+?  fails to  22...Kf8  23.Rd3-+  And now Black has the zwischenzug  23...Be7! }
22... Qe5 23. f7+
{ No credit for other moves. Black's king was threatening to run with Kd8. }
23... Kf8 24. Rg3
{ Threatening Qd8#.   24.Qd8+  Kg7  25.Rg3+  nearly works. But  25...Qxg3-+ }
24... Bb6
{ The pacifying   24...Nf6  fails too.  25.Rxf6!  h5   25...Bd7  26.Rg8+  Rxg8  27.fxg8=Q+  Kxg8  28.Qg4+  Kh7  29.Bd3++-   25...Qxe2  26.Rg8+  Rxg8  27.fxg8=Q+  Kxg8  28.Qg3++-  26.Rff3  Bd7  27.Rg5  Qd4  28.Rg8+  Rxg8  29.fxg8=Q+  Kxg8  30.Qg5+  Qg7  31.Qxc5+- }
25. Bd3
{ What a move! Down two pieces, White takes his time and improves his bishop, but what is White's idea here? }
25... Bc7 26. Bh7
{ That's it. White is protecting g8 and cutting of the defence of h6. } 26...
Nf6 27. Qxh6+
{ 27.Rg8+?  is the game continuation, but since White found the amazing combination up to here and the game notation doesn't make a lot of sense from here on, that might be a error in the notation.  27...Kxf7  28.Rxf6+  Qxf6  29.Bg6+  Qxg6  30.Qe7+-+  1-0 }
27... Ke7 { It's still not obvious what White is doing here. } 28. Rg8
{ 28.f8=Q+?  Rxf8  29.Rg7+  Rf7  30.Bg6  Rxg7  31.Qxg7+  Kd6-+ } 28... Rxg8 29.
Qxf6+ { 29.fxg8=Q  Nxg8  30.Bxg8  Bd7-+  is nothing for White. } 29... Qxf6 30.
fxg8=N+
{ Amazing. After 9 forced moves, White gets an endgame a pawn to the good. Additionally, Black's king is weak and he has problems developing his queenside. White is winning. }
*

